==Ancient Greek==

===Etymology===
From (a presumed derivative of) [[γένος]] {{GG|1085}}; 

===Pronunciation===
*γενεά / genea / ghen-eh-ah'

===Noun===
'''γενεά'''

# a generation; by implication an age (the period or the persons): - [[age]], [[generation]], [[nation]], [[time]].

